lead_paragraph: Kei Nishikori and Juan Martin del Potro won in straight sets at the Swiss Indoors on Wednesday to stay on course for a quarterfinals meeting.

headline.print_headline: Nishikori, Del Potro Advance Easily at Swiss Indoors
